exports.insertAfter = function (newNode, ref) {

exports.getBoundingClientRect = function (el) {
  var r = el.getBoundingClientRect()
  return {
    left: r.left,
    top: r.top,
    right: r.left + r.width,
    bottom: r.top + r.height
  }
}
